<h2>Gears of War 4 - 98%</h2>
<h4>Great and Difficult Shooter</h4>
<p>Gears of War 4 is a fantastic and well designed 3rd person shooter. The world that Gears takes place in is unforgiving. This is a fresh new start for the franchise but with some familiar faces thrown in. The campaign is a 5 hour action packed affair. Graphics are fresh and evolving throughout the acts. The only downfall is the glitch laiden multiplayer which I am sure will be fixed.</p>

